    <definition>The Audio_Video class contains metadata for Encoded_Audio or Encoded_Video data. 
      Most attributes are taken directly from the EXIF/XMP keywords often found in A/V files. If 
      there is any ambiguity in the definitions, refer to the EXIF/XMP standards for clarification.  
      This metadata herein is not intended to be comprehensive; it is a subset of the available metadata, 
